<!-- OPERATIONAL IMPROVEMENTS -->
<div class="s">
<div class="sh"><h2>Operational improvements</h2><span class="p pt">Shipping in Q2</span></div>
<div class="g3">
<div class="cc">
<div class="ct">NowPayments batch deposits</div>
<div class="prose">
<p>Deposit funding is now automated via NowPayments batch CSV uploads. The master operations sheet generates a batch file with amounts set 10% above minimum thresholds to absorb fees and slippage.</p>
<p><strong>Impact:</strong> Eliminates manual wallet-by-wallet funding. A batch of 8+ deposits can be submitted in one action instead of individually. Reduces deposit turnaround from days to hours.</p>
<p><strong>Status:</strong> Live on the master ops sheet. Batch generation, status tracking, and freelancer sheet sync all automated via GAS.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="cc">
<div class="ct">QC-gated payment model</div>
<div class="prose">
<p>Replacing hourly pay with per-trace, QC-approved payments. Freelancers get paid only for traces that pass QC with complete metadata. Upwork contracts convert from hourly to fixed-price milestones.</p>
<p><strong>Rates:</strong> New entity deposit $5.00, additional deposit $3.50, withdrawal $4.00, withdrawal PSP $4.50, entity research (pre-approved) $1.50, metadata bonus $0.50/trace.</p>
<p><strong>Impact:</strong> Aligns pay with output. Feb simulation showed high-output tracers earning more, low-output/high-hour tracers earning less. Eliminates the $38-45/trace outliers.</p>
<p><strong>Status:</strong> Proposal complete. Pending budget sign-off from Lucy/Rhea. Pilot planned with 2-3 Upwork freelancers in April.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="cc">
<div class="ct">Sheet automations</div>
<div class="prose">
<p>The master operations sheet now syncs status changes bidirectionally with freelancer sheets. When a deposit is marked sent on master, it updates the freelancer's Transactions tab automatically.</p>
<p><strong>Ingestion sweep:</strong> 6-hour time-driven sweep of all freelancer sheets for QC Ready rows, with deduplication and append to the master ingestion sheet.</p>
<p><strong>Fee tracker:</strong> 12-file GAS codebase recovering blockchain dates and fees via block explorer APIs across 25+ chains.</p>
<p><strong>Next:</strong> Weekly metrics script auto-calculates TVS, WIS, and traces per hour for every freelancer each Monday. QC quality tracking to be integrated once per-trace model is live.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
