<!-- Q2 OUTLOOK -->
<div class="s">
<div class="sh"><h2>Q2 outlook</h2></div>
<div class="prose">
<p>Entity discovery will be deprioritised for Q2. The focus shifts to retracing already-traced entities with withdrawal-heavy batches. This directly addresses the C2 bottleneck: retrace work scores higher on C2 than first-time discovery, and when weighted toward withdrawals, it lifts both C1 and C2 simultaneously.</p>
<p>QC-gated payments, once approved, will add a QC pass rate metric to future reports. The target is 90%+ first-time pass rate (KR1). This will appear as a new section in the Q2 dashboard alongside TVS and WIS.</p>
<p>The NowPayments batch system and sheet automations are already live. The remaining automation gap is the weekly metrics script, which will eliminate manual data collection for these reports.</p>
</div>
</div>

